Class HuffmanCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • HuffmanCode

  • public class HuffmanCode
extends Object
    Implementation of Huffman coding. An instance of stores a code used for subsequent encoding and decoding of strings.
    Version:
    17 October 2016
    Author:
    Bennett Alex Myers
